title: Mick Fanning - 3 x ASP World Champion - 2013
description:
After a very successful and consistent year on tour, Mick Fanning was crowned the 2013 ASP World Champion. The title race between Mick and Kelly Slater came down to the final event in Hawaii. In pumping clean waves, the guys took to the water and surfed like absolute champions. Mick had to make the Semi Finals to take the crown and in the dying minutes of his Quarter Final he did exactly that. We couldn't be more stoked for Mick. Congratulations.

Music: Silver Bullets Music
Track: Armed and Dangerous
Source: Getty Images
